node.text: One more from @sls so excited for the Salt Lake City stop in about 4 weeks!

node.text: So stoked and so grateful to have won the @sls street league qualifier this weekend. So many unreal moments. Huge congrats to @lucasrabelo & @alecmajerus  as well. They absolutely slayed it. ❤️‍🔥

node.text: What a moment for me. Last try, for a 9.2. Got my first and second 9 clubs ever in the Olympics. Thank you so much for the clip @nnieguglia ❤️🙏🏽 @teamcanada @canadaskateboard @olympics

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Micky Papa on July 24, 2021 tagging @olympics, @teamcanada, and @canadaskateboard. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: What a journey it’s been to get to this moment. All I got to say is to everyone that’s helped me and shown me love along the way I appreciate you more than you know and to the haters thanks for the fuel. ⛽️ @teamcanada @olympics
